    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Cytos Biotechnology AG</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to test the efficacy of a vaccine against house dust mite and/or
      cat allergy compared to placebo in adult patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
